ate a novel route to\nmaximize the PCE of halide perovskite indoor photovoltaic devices and their\npotential for application in the IoT industry.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Jan 2023 17:19:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-01"}
