 trustworthy theory. Our theory has 28\npropositions representing this model that map properties to the constructs of\nour theory. The operationalization generated 34 testable hypotheses, and we\nthoroughly tested 11 of them. The testing has proved the effectiveness of the\ntheoretical framework, while the operationalization of the constructs has\nenhanced the initial framework.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Jan 2023 19:05:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-02"}
