ogan and Soergel)\nfrom a coherent form (a real counterpart to Fargues' conjecture): the tamely\nramified geometric Langlands conjecture on the twistor line, which we survey.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Jan 2023 19:19:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-02"}
