nstant (60$^{\\circ}$), while the face-on\nangular width increases from 96$^{\\circ}$ to 114$^{\\circ}$, indicating a\nlateral expansion. The latitude of the CME source region decreases slightly\nfrom $\\sim$18$^{\\circ}$ to $\\sim$13$^{\\circ}$, implying an equatorward\ndeflection during propagation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Feb 2023 03:40:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-15"}
