 with follow-up HST imaging at\nlate times, when the SN has sufficiently faded. This potential use of JWST\nopens a new era of identifying SN progenitor candidates at high spatial\nresolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Feb 2023 06:37:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-02"}
