ith no evidence of\nspectroscopic binarity. These are the preferred targets for follow-up\nspectroscopy to measure alpha.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Feb 2023 12:25:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-10"}
