 implications of HIPs on calculations\nwith meta-GGA functionals with a number of recent meta-GGA functionals, and\nfind most Minnesota functionals to be ill-behaved. We also examine the\npotential usefulness of the explicit control over the derivative in HIPs for\nforming numerical atomic orbital basis sets, but find that confining potentials\nare still likely a better option.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Feb 2023 13:38:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 26 Mar 2023 11:08:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 21 Apr 2023 08:11:43 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 26 Apr 2023 08:03:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-28"}
