 distribution functions. The measured cross sections are well described\nby the fixed-order QCD predictions within the experimental and theoretical\nuncertainties in most of the investigated phase-space region.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Feb 2023 15:33:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-02"}
